jdh97t sends:

> assuming I have rust

Assuming you have a drill you can put a flapwheel sander on, or a little
angle grinder, or some other means of sanding cars, I'd grind the rust off,
put a little primer on it (a brush works) and paint over the primer with
brushable Rustoleum. Not pretty, but better than rust.
